*sbcl-0.8.11 (14 Jun 2004)

  14 Jun 2004; <mkennedy@gentoo.org> +files/0.8.11/README.Gentoo,
  +files/0.8.11/customize-target-features.lisp,
  +files/0.8.11/customize-target-features.lisp.no-threads,
