*sbcl-0.8.8 (27 Feb 2004)

  27 Feb 2004; <mkennedy@gentoo.org> sbcl-0.8.8.ebuild,
  files/0.8.8/README.Gentoo, files/0.8.8/customize-target-features.lisp,
